{"tid":248808,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬逢國：不如復活節減一日假... 孔誕補返日畀你哋","createTime":"2017-05-18T23:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T01:11:37.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3c7cab171227aa0faf21b8852c3746b855b1cb","tid":248808,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:59:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">近年有聲音要求將紀念孔子的孔聖誕列為公眾假期，前日（5月17日）立法會會議上，又有相關的提問。馬逢國議員向勞工及福利局局長蕭偉強查詢，政府有否意思刪減「復活節星期一」，而增加「孔聖誕日」公眾假期，但看來這個訴求未見有太大支持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201705/20170517ggg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201705%2F20170517ggg.png&h=bb219b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-17-2017/37908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F05-17-2017%2F37908&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=e8e647ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-17-2017/37908</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2017<br />\n<br />\n馬逢國提到，特首曾於2014年表示孔子是「萬世師表」，對中國歷史和社會影響深遠，而他提出的「仁義禮智信」是中華民族的核心價值，值得弘揚推廣。馬逢國指出，鑑於有孔教領袖建議每年的公眾假期增訂「孔聖誕日」，並刪減「復活節星期一」以維持每年的公眾假期總日數不變，而該建議據悉已獲得其餘五大宗教的領袖支持，故希望當局表態。<br />\n<br />\n蕭偉強回應指，公眾假期的現有安排是經過多年廣泛諮詢後而訂定，任何修訂《公眾假期條例》的建議均會對社會各界帶來深遠的影響，必須在取得社會廣泛支持及明確共識後方能推行。他續指，由於有關訂立「孔聖誕日」為公眾假期並刪減「復活節星期一」的建議至今未見有社會廣泛的訴求，故此我們須小心處理有關事宜。<br />\n<br />\n蕭偉強補充時提到，政府支持孔教團體自2014年起，將每年9月第3個星期日訂為「孔聖誕日」，以慶祝孔子誕辰，並傳揚儒家文化。</div>"},{"pid":"cdc5eea06fcab610f673289b5c321fd47dad094e","tid":248808,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:06:24.000Z","msg":"旅遊界第一個屌鬼啦。<br />\n<br />\ncut 年初三好過啦"},{"pid":"b2bcef2d255464e8406397bc8e2bbd78c9bd95f2","tid":248808,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:16:52.000Z","msg":"點睇當初批林批孔的人而家又走去推崇儒家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79a5dbc3c4248414adf61f96827dc9b28b64180","tid":248808,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:29:19.000Z","msg":"應該新增一個 唔應該取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848c03f12ec3675d30c16da9810bfa7b701c4b46","tid":248808,"uid":64225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:30:48.000Z","msg":"孔子，教蓄一個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n值唔值呀"},{"pid":"65d7fdf255b73073766d13acca7bc14575d48dfe","tid":248808,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>孔子，教蓄一個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n值唔值呀</blockquote><br />\n孔老2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9836c1a6ae61b61dfd255f4f33e683ee73037fe0","tid":248808,"uid":78178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:41:31.000Z","msg":"on9既，想人支持就應該直接加一日<br />\n一換一都冇著數邊個會理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485641a472acf8516ddbf2ee38a49869163f568a","tid":248808,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:43:09.000Z","msg":"一換一姐係多鳩魚"},{"pid":"7fc66bc45572c42b8bda2ef397dec45a07afad74","tid":248808,"uid":1286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:43:09.000Z","msg":"復活節一定有一日係星期六<br />\n就減果日啦"},{"pid":"fcc296f77f8425d54026e3e4c31f4a174ba85df2","tid":248808,"uid":22141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:47:27.000Z","msg":"痴線 加一日啦on9"},{"pid":"76d1b38e552063bc4989c545bb5a53fce42beb73","tid":248808,"uid":49359,"like